    "GODoc is a protein function prediction method that utilizes TFPSSM(Term Frequency based on PSSM) features (Liu et al., 2020).",
    "PANNZER (Törönen and Holm, 2022) is another tool for predicting protein function using weighted KNN classifiers, designed for automated function prediction tasks and supporting genome-level queries."
